## 📦 Phase 5: Build & Publish

### Prompt 5.1: CI/CD Setup

```
Create GitHub Actions workflows for my ZenUI monorepo.

Workflows needed:

1. CI (on push/PR):
   - Install dependencies (pnpm)
   - Lint all packages
   - Type check all packages
   - Run tests
   - Build all packages

2. Release (on version tag):
   - Build all packages
   - Publish to npm with provenance
   - Create GitHub release

3. Preview Deployments (on PR):
   - Build docs site
   - Deploy to Vercel preview

Create:
- .github/workflows/ci.yml
- .github/workflows/release.yml
- .github/workflows/preview.yml

Use pnpm and caching for speed.
```

